n%20a%20rise%20in%20interest%20from%20contractors%20on%20their%20platforms.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20spent%20%2414.3%20billion%20to%20acquire%20nearly%20half%20of%20Scale%20AI%20and%20level%20up%20in%20the%20AI%20race%20%E2%80%94%20but%20the%20startup's%20rivals%20spy%20an%20opportunity%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExecutives%20at%20five%20Scale%20AI%20competitors%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20they%20have%20seen%20a%20big%20uptick%20in%20client%20inquiries%20%E2%80%94%20but%20declined%20to%20provide%20numbers%20%E2%80%94%20and%20job%20interest%20since%20the%20Meta%20deal%20was%20announced%20on%20June%2013.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20now%20holds%20a%2049%25%20stake%20in%20a%20company%20handling%20AI%20training%20data%20for%20many%20of%20its%20competitors%2C%20like%20Google%2C%20OpenAI%2C%20and%20xAI.%20In%20response%2C%20those%20three%20companies%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-xai-openai-pull-back-meta-scale-ai-investment-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epaused%20at%20least%20some%20of%20their%20work%20with%20Scale%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Independence%20from%20Big%20Tech%20has%20now%20become%20a%20core%20part%20of%20the%20pitch%20for%20rival%20AI%20training%20companies%20vying%20for%20those%20contracts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscale.com%2Fblog%2Fcustomer-trust-scale-meta-deal%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eblog%20post%3C%2Fa%3E%20following%20the%20Meta%20deal%2C%20Scale%20AI%20reassured%20clients%20that%20it%20remains%20a%20%26quot%3Bneutral%2C%20independent%20partner.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERyan%20Kolln%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20data%20annotation%20firm%20Appen%2C%20told%20BI%20the%20deal%20would%20%26quot%3Bcreate%20a%20pretty%20big%20disruption%20to%20our%20industry%20and%20create%20huge%20opportunities%20for%20Appen%20and%20our%20peers%20to%20fill%20the%20hole%20that's%20going%20to%20be%20left%20by%20Scale.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20added%20pitch%20is%2C%20'hey%2C%20we%20are%20a%20publicly%20listed%20company%20and%20we're%20really%20focused%20on%20data%20neutrality%2C'%26quot%3B%20added%20Kolln%2C%20whose%20company%20counts%20Amazon%20and%20Nvidia%20as%20clients.%20%26quot%3BOur%20customers%20are%20really%20evaluating%20their%20vendor%20ecosystem.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUK-based%20Prolific%2C%20which%20provides%20vetted%20freelancers%20for%20academic%20and%20commercial%20AI%20research%2C%20is%20also%20using%20neutrality%20as%20a%20selling%20point%2C%20its%20CEO%2C%20Phelim%20Bradley%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20build%20models.%20We%20don't%20compete%20with%20our%20customers.%20We%20don't%20have%20conflicting%20incentives%2C%26quot%3B%20Bradley%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20clients%20are%20now%20reluctant%20to%20go%20all%20in%20on%20a%20single%20AI%20training%20provider.%20Big%20companies%20often%20spread%20their%20work%20among%20vendors%2C%20like%20cloud%20providers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BScale%20benefited%20a%20lot%20from%20their%20awareness%20and%20being%20synonymous%20with%20data%20labeling%20for%20Big%20Tech%2C%26quot%3B%20Bradley%20said.%20%26quot%3BNow%2C%20it's%20a%20much%20easier%20question%20to%20answer%3A%20'How%20are%20you%20different%20from%20Scale%3F'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Scale%20AI%20spokesperson%20told%20BI%20that%20%26quot%3Bnothing%20has%20changed%26quot%3B%20about%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fscale-ai-public-google-docs-security-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecustomer%20data%20protection%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20this%20confusion%20is%20being%20driven%20by%20smaller%20competitors%20who%20seek%20to%20gain%20from%20promoting%20false%20claims%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20added.%20%26quot%3BSecurity%20and%20customer%20trust%20have%20always%20been%20core%20to%20our%20business%2C%20and%20we%20will%20continue%20to%20ensure%20the%20right%20protections%20are%20in%20place%20to%20help%20safeguard%20all%20of%20our%20work%20with%20customers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJonathan%20Siddharth%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Turing%2C%20which%20trains%20models%20for%20major%20AI%20labs%20including%20Meta%2C%20Anthropic%2C%20and%20Google%2C%20said%20that%20discussions%20with%20customers%20have%20increased%20tenfold%20as%20frontier%20labs%20realize%20they%20need%20%26quot%3Btop%20talent%20and%20impartial%20partners.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLabs%20increasingly%20want%20a%20Switzerland-like%20collaborator%20%E2%80%94%20someone%20model-agnostic%20%E2%80%94%20who%20can%20help%20them%20win%20the%20AGI%20race%2C%20rather%20than%20being%20tied%20to%20a%20single%20player%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20artificial%20general%20intelligence.%20He%20added%20that%20data%20annotation%20companies%20are%20often%20working%20on%20the%20exact%20capabilities%20that%20differentiate%20one%20AI%20model%20from%20another.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229a2845d9-7947-4f7c-a263-2cd10908c8b7%5C%22%3ETalent%20war%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EScale%20AI's%20competitors%20are%20also%20moving%20to%20pick%20up%20its%20freelance%20workers%2C%20some%20of%20whom%20have%20had%20projects%20they%20are%20working%20on%20paused%20after%20clients%20like%20Google%20halted%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScale%20has%20at%20least%20240%2C00%20gig%20workers%20globally%20who%20conduct%20AI%20training%20projects%2C%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fscale-ai-outlier-training-harmful-ai-prompts-2025-04%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eflagging%20harmful%20chatbot%20responses%3C%2Fa%3E.%20After%20some%20of%20Scale%20AI's%20projects%20were%20paused%2C%20the%20market%20became%20flooded%20with%20freelancers%20looking%20for%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESapien%20AI%20CEO%20Rowan%20Stone%20told%20BI%20that%20his%20company%20had%2040%2C000%20new%20annotators%20join%20within%2048%20hours%20of%20Meta's%20Scale%20AI%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20servers%20are%20currently%20melting%2C%26quot%3B%20Stone%20said%20last%20week.%20%26quot%3BOur%20engineering%20team%20spent%20the%20entire%20weekend%20bolstering%20load%20balancers%2C%20spinning%20up%20new%20infrastructure%2C%20and%20getting%20us%20ready%20for%20the%20load%20that%20we're%20seeing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20these%20new%20sign-ups%20were%20from%20India%20and%20the%20Philippines%20%E2%80%94%20regions%20where%20Scale%20AI%20had%20long%20been%20a%20leader%2C%20Stone%20added.%20%26quot%3BThe%20change%20in%20user%20signup%20pattern%20coincides%20pretty%20neatly%20with%20the%20Scale%20news%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Alexandr%20Wang%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F684ae50ef748d8c055f38f41%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221666%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EScale%20AI%20founder%20Alexandr%20Wang%20has%20moved%20to%20a%20leadership%20role%20at%20Meta's%20new%20superintelligence%20division.%3Cp%3EJeff%20Chiu%2FAP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMercor%20AI's%20head%20of%20product%2C%20Osvald%20Nitski%2C%20said%20that%20the%20startup%20has%20received%20applications%20from%20full-time%20Scale%20employees%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BOur%20hiring%20bar%20is%20extremely%20high%20%E2%80%94%20we're%20only%20taking%20the%20best%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMercor%20says%20it%20works%20with%20six%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BMagnificent%20Seven%26quot%3B%20tech%20companies%20and%20is%20picking%20up%20projects%20from%20clients%20leaving%20Scale.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20terms%20of%20contractors%2C%20Nitski%20said%20the%20company%20is%20focused%20on%20recruiting%20elite-level%20annotators%2C%20like%20International%20Math%20Olympiad%20medalists%2C%20Rhodes%20Scholars%2C%20and%20Ph.D.%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENitski%20said%20it's%20been%20a%20busy%20two%20weeks%20at%20Mercor%2C%20as%20it%20