lcohol%2C%20and%20sets%20them%20ablaze%2C%20is%20a%20beloved%20component%20of%20the%20chain's%20razzle-dazzle%20culinary%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELaunched%20last%20month%2C%20the%20lunch%20deal%20comes%20with%20a%20guarantee%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.benihana.com%2Fmenus%2Fpower-lunch%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ein%20and%20out%20in%2045%20minutes%20for%20less%20than%20twenty%20bucks%20or%20your%20meal%20is%20free%3C%2Fa%3E.%20One%20might%20expect%20commensurate%20constraints%20on%20the%20creative%20freedom%20of%20the%20chef.%20But%20Benihana%2C%20which%20opened%20in%201964%20and%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.benihana.com%2Flocations%2F%3Fcountry%3Dunited-states%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Earound%3C%2Fa%3E%20100%20locations%20or%20offshoots%20nationwide%2C%20appears%20to%20have%20remembered%20that%20its%20customers%20come%20for%20the%20show%20just%20as%20much%20as%20the%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20sat%20at%20the%20teppanyaki%20table%20on%20a%20recent%20weekday%2C%20surrounded%20by%20around%20a%20dozen%20diners%20that%20fell%20exclusively%20into%20three%20categories%20(children%2C%20parents%2C%20and%20office%20workers)%2C%20I%20watched%20our%20chef%2C%20a%20tall%20man%20bedecked%20in%20bracelets%20and%20a%20heavy%20silver%20ring%2C%20toss%20onion%20rings%20onto%20a%20steaming%20grill.%20He%20coated%20them%20with%20oil%20and%20booze%20and%20readied%20a%20lighter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22onion%20volcano%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685ef63af748d8c055f49238%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMagical.%3Cp%3EKate%20Taylor%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20a%20Benihana%20newbie%2C%20and%20I%20had%20been%20briefed%20on%20what%20might%20happen.%20Still%2C%20I%20was%20overcome%20with%20delight%20when%20the%20mushroom-shaped%20flame%20shot%20