by%20in%20the%20house.%20Not%20for%20once%20did%20I%20stop%20to%20think%20that%20what%20I%20was%20feeling%20could%20be%20the%20result%20of%20something%20else%20happening%20within%20the%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EOn%20the%20day%20of%20the%20heart%20attack%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20Monday%20morning%2C%20and%20I%20was%20getting%20into%20the%20week%20after%20having%20spent%20a%20very%20good%20weekend%20with%20my%20wife%20and%20child.%20I%20woke%20up%20as%20usual%20at%20around%206.00%20am%20and%20by%207.30%20am%20I%20started%20getting%20ready%20for%20work.%20By%209.30%20a%2Cm%20I%20was%20done%20with%20breakfast%2C%20which%20was%20my%20standard%20dalia%20porridge.%20In%20the%20next%20half%20an%20hour%2Cr%20I%20was%20in%20the%20office%20at%20my%20desk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20cold%20day%20in%20Bhopal%2C%20and%20as%20I%20parked%20my%20car%20in%20the%20office%20parking%20lot%20and%20started%20walking%20towards%20the%20building%2C%20I%20felt%20very%20uneasy.%20I%20started%20to%20feel%20breathless%3B%20I%20got%20to%20my%20seat%2C%20sat%20down%2C%20and%20opened%20up%20my%20laptop%20to%20start%20the%20day.%20Through%20all%20this%2Cs%20I%20was%20feeling%20breathless%20and%20eventually%20I%20reclined%20my%20chair%20and%20started%20actively%20trying%20to%20get%20in%20more%20breaths.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENothing%20helped.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20watch%20on%20my%20left%20hand%20started%20feeling%20heavy%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20left%20hand%2C%20on%20which%20I%20had%20worn%20a%20watch%2C%20was%20feeling%20so%20heavy%20that%20I%20was%20unable%20to%20even%20lift%20it.%20Soon%20after%2C%20I%20started%20feeling%20a%20%E2%80%9