erindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FWhatsApp-Image-2020-10-05-at-5.12.00-PM-1751272476.jpeg%20960w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-458069%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EAt%2033%2C%20the%20last%20thing%20Ram%20was%20expecting%20was%20a%20heart%20attack.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%20this%20time%2C%20my%20colleagues%20started%20noticing%20my%20discomfort.%20The%20doctor%20in%20the%20office%20was%20called%20in%20and%20asked%20my%20colleagues%20to%20rush%20me%20to%20the%20hospital%20since%20my%20pulse%20rate%20was%20falling.%20I%20was%20put%20on%20a%20chair%20with%20wheels%2C%20and%20my%20colleagues%20managed%20to%20wheel%20me%20out%20of%20the%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hospital%20was%20about%20fifteen%20minutes%20away%2C%20and%20that%20period%20was%20extremely%20uncomfortable%20for%20me.%20I%20was%20in%20and%20out%20of%20consciousness%2C%20but%20all%20through%20kept%20telling%20myself%20to%20take%20long%20breaths.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWheeled%20into%20the%20emergency%20room%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20was%20able%20to%20comprehend%20and%20answer%20most%20of%20the%20questions%20that%20the%20doctors%20were%20asking%20me.%20I%20even%20remember%20giving%20my%20phone%20passcode%20to%20a%20colleague%20so%20they%20could%20call%20and%20inform%20my%20wife%20about%20my%20condition.%20My%20ECG%20was%20the%20first%20thing%20that%20was%C2%A0checked%2C%C2%A0and%20that%20was%20when%20they%20found%20that%20I%20had%20suffered%20a%20heart%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20was%20wheeled%20into%20the%20operating%20theatre%2C%20and%20an%20emergency%20surgery%20was%20done.%20The%20pain%20that%20had%20started%20from%20my%20left%20hand%20had%20now%20spread%20all%20over%20my%20body%2C%20and%20I%20felt%20as%20though%20I%20had%20been%20given%20an%20electric%20shock.%20The%20LAD%20artery%2C%20considered%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20three%20most%20important%20coronary%20arteries%20in%20the%20body%2C%20was%20completely%20blocked%2C%20and%20the%20doctors%20mentioned%20post-surgery%20that%20what%20I%20had%20experienced%20was%20a%20major%20heart%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EImmense%20pain%20during%20the%20surgery%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20level%20of%20pain%20I%20experienced%20all%20through%20is%20not%20something%20that%20I%20can%20even%20put%20in%20words.%20It%20was%20only%20after%20about%20an%20hour%20or%20so%20post-surgery%20that%20I%20felt%20some%20kind%20of%20relief%20from%20the%20pain.%20There%20were%20two%20stents%20that%20were%20placed%20in%20the%20LAD%20artery%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20angiography%20was%20done%2C%20there%20were%20other%20blockages%20also%20that%20were%20found.%20I%20had%20almost%2095%20per%20cent%20blockages%20in%20other%20arteries%2C%20and%20therefore%2C%20I%20was%20advised%20to%20go%20through%20yet%20another%20angioplasty%20as%20soon%20as%20possible%20to%20fix%20those%20blockages%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPost%20the%20surgeries%2C%20I%20was%20put%20on%20various%20medications%2C%20and%20I%20pop%20in%20at%20least%20ten%20pills%20a%20day%20now.%20From%20medicines%20for%20blood%20pressure%20to%20cholesterol%20and%20blood%20thinners%2C%20I%20have%20been%20prescribed%20so%20many.%20None%20of%20which%20I%20needed%20to%20take%20pre-surgery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3