400.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FWhatsApp-Image-2020-10-05-at-4.51.31-PM-1751272527-150x200.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FWhatsApp-Image-2020-10-05-at-4.51.31-PM-1751272527-640x853.jpeg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FWhatsApp-Image-2020-10-05-at-4.51.31-PM-1751272527.jpeg%20960w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-458071%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ERam%20celebrating%20his%2033rd%20birthday.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20year%20before%20my%20heart%20attack%2C%20I%20was%20very%20regular%20at%20the%20gym%2C%20could%20be%20able%20to%20run%20on%20the%20treadmill%2C%20and%20even%20my%20stamina%20levels%20were%20very%20good.%20Even%20a%20few%20months%20before%20the%20heart%20attack%2C%20I%20could%20comfortably%20climb%20up%20to%20six%20floors%20without%20huffing%20and%20puffing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20never%20felt%20that%20I%20had%20any%20physical%20symptoms%2C%20especially%20with%20regard%20to%20my%20breathing%20or%20ability%20to%20work%20out%2C%20until%20two%20months%20before%20the%20heart%20attack.%20I%20had%20lost%20a%20good%20amount%20of%20weight%20by%20doing%20strength%20training%2C%20weights%2C%20and%20cardio.%20After%20the%20heart%20attack%2C%20my%20trainers%20at%20the%20gym%20were%20surprised%20and%20even%20shocked%20that%20I%20could%20have%20gone%20through%20something%20like%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E2%20months%20before%20the%20heart%20attack%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20think%20back%2C%20there%20were%20some%20symptoms.%20I%20started%20feeling%20dizzy%20after%20small%20physical%20movements%2C%20for%20example%2C%20when%20I%20would%20get%20out%20of%20my%20car%20and%20walk%20towards%20my%20office%20building.%20However%2C%20it%20would%20pass%20quickly%2C%20and%20therefore%20I%20did%20not%20give%20it%20much%20thought.%20Looking%20back%2C%20I%20remember%20feeling%20bloated%20on%20several%20occasions%2C%20and%20when%20I%20look%20at%20old%20pictures%2C%20I%20am%20able%20to%20make%20that%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Ffeatured-img-9_11zon-1-1751272632.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Life%20was%20as%20good%20as%20could%20be%20until%20the%20heart%20attack.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Ffeatured-img-9_11zon-1-1751272632.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Ffeatured-img-9_11zon-1-1751272632-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Ffeatured-img-9_11zon-1-1751272632-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Ffeatured-img-9_11zon-1-1751272632-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Ffeatured-img-9_11zon-1-1751272632-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-458076%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ELife%20was%20as%20good%20as%20it%20could%20be%20until%20the%20heart%20attack.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20also%20started%20developing%20a%20lot%20of%20dark%20circles%20around%20the%20same%20time.%20Frequent%20headaches%20during%20the%20last%20three%20months%20were%20also%20a%20given.%20However%2C%20all%20this%20can%20also%20very%20well%20be%20attributed%20to%20being%20a%20new%20parent%20and%20could%20be%20a%20side%20effect%20of%20not%20getting%20enough%20rest%20and%20having%20to%20wake%20up%20at%20all%20odd%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20almost%20seven%20years%2C%20I%20have%20been%20prone%20to%20acidity%2C%20and%20that%20ensured%20that%20I%20ate%20healthy%20and%20had%20most%20of%20my%20meals%20at%20home.%20I%20tried%20not%20to%20miss%20my%20meals%20or%20change%20the%20times%20of%20the%20meals%20too%20much%20to%20ensure%20that%20I%20stayed%20fine.%20I%20did%20consult%20a%20doctor%2Cr%20and%20it%20was%20diagnosed%20to%20be%20GERD%2C%20a%20gastric-related%20issue%2C%20wherein%20the%20stomach%20produces%20more%20acid%20than%20needed.%20With%20medications%2C%20the%20symptoms%20would%20decrease%2C%20but%20it%20was%20something%20that%20kept%20coming%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20after%20my%20heart%20attack%2C%20doctors%20mentioned%20that%20I%20was%20perhaps%20confusing%20the%20angina%20pain%20to%20be%20acidity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMy%20biggest%20takeaway%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20me%2C%20this%20entire%20episode%20reiterated%20the%20fact%20that%20we%20take%20our%20bodies%20for%20granted.%20We%20have%20a%20very%20typical%20notion%20that%20until%20and%20unless%20one%20is%20about%2040%20or%2045%20years%20of%20age%2C%20medical%20issues%20do%20not%20crop%20up%2C%20and%20especially%20not%20ailments%20related%20to%20the%20heart.%20I%20was%20conscious%20about%20working%20out%2C%20eating%20right%2C%20and%20doing%20everything%20to%20stay%20fit%2C%20and%20yet%20I%20suffered%20a%20heart%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Ffeatured-img-10_11zon-1751272717.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Six%20months%20after%20Ram%E2%80%99s%20heart%20attack.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Ffeatured-img-10_11zon-1751272717.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Ffeatured-img-10_11zon-1751272717-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Ffeatured-img-10_11zon-1751272717-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Ffeatured-img-10_11zon-1751272717-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Ffeatured-img-10_11zon-1751272717-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-458077%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESix%20months%20after%20Ram%E2%80%99s%20heart%20attack.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20do%20not%20know%20what%20is%20going%20on%20within%20our%20bodies%2C%20and%20that%20is%20what%20I%20have%20learnt%2C%20albeit%20the%20hard%20way.%20Age%20is%20not%20something%20that%20can%20be%20linked%20to%20a%20heart%20attack.%20So%20many%20factors%2C%20which%20include%20lifestyle%20and%20genetics%2C%20play%20a%20part%20in%20it.%20It%20is%20almost%20like%20we%20are%20sitting%20on%20a%20time-bomb%2C%20and%20until%20it%20goes%20of%2Cf%20everything%20is%20fine%2C%20so%20the%20best%20way%20to%20help%20yourself%20is%20periodic%20health%20checks%20and%20monitoring%20all%20health%20parameters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%93%20Ram%2C%20As%20Told%20To%20Vidya%20Raja%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDoctor%20speaks%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Subash%20Chandhar%20(MD%2C%20DM)%2C%20a%20practising%20cardiologist%20at%20the%20Venkateswara%20Hospital%2C%20Chennai%2C%20helps%20us%20understand%20what%20a%20heart%20attack%20is%20and%20how%20we%20can%20stay%20alert.%20In%20this%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F191206%2Fcardiac-arrest-symptoms-emergency-care-treatment-cardiologist-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Earticle%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CDuring%20a%20heart%20attack%2C%20the%20patient%E2%80%99s%20heart%20loses