%22%3A%22Meet%20The%20Odia%20Creators%20Using%20Social%20Media%20%26amp%3B%20Humour%20to%20Reframe%20Climate%20Conversations%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CPrakruti%20badaluchi%20(Nature%20is%20changing).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20common%20consensus%20among%20locals%20in%20rural%20Odisha.%20Terms%20like%20%E2%80%98climate%20change%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98global%20warming%E2%80%99%20have%20yet%20to%20enter%20their%20everyday%20lexicon%2C%20as%20content%20creator%20Soumya%20Ranjan%20Sahoo%20(26)%20remarked%20during%20the%20time%20he%20spent%20with%20them%2C%20attempting%20to%20document%20their%20stories.%20When%20he%20asked%20them%20where%20they%20were%20drawing%20their%20conclusions%20from%2C%20they%20invited%20him%20for%20lunch.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20rural%20India%2C%20his%20hosts%20explained%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3Ethali%20%3C%2Fem%3E(food%20platter)%20is%20a%20canvas%3B%20it%20reflects%20the%20tangible%20impact%20of%20atmospheric%20shifts.%20While%20once%2C%20violets%20and%20greens%20and%20reds%20danced%20across%20the%20table%20%E2%80%94%20credit%20goes%20to%20the%20varied%20seasonal%20produce%20%E2%80%94%20now%20it%E2%80%99s%20just%20monochromes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20locals%20told%20me%20that%20seasonal%20vegetables%20are%20no%20longer%20available%20in%20the%20markets%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Soumya%2C%20whose%20growing-up%20years%20in%20Sambalpur%2C%20Odisha%2C%20have%20given%20him%20a%20sound%20sense%20of%20local%20produce.%20%E2%80%9CNot%20only%20are%20the%20seasons%20delayed%2C%20they%20say%2C%20but%20even%20when%20they%20do%20arrive%2C%20they%20lack%20their%20characteristics%3B%20it%20rains%20in%20winter%2C%20summers%20are%20unbearably%20hot%2C%20and%20monsoons%20often%20pause%20to%20make%20way%20for%20%E2%80%98a%20summer%E2%80%99%20in%20between.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20cities%2C%20we%20call%20this%20global%20warming%2C%20a%20reality%20that%20the%20United%20Nations%20is%20racing%20against%20time%20to%20cap%20at%201.5%20degrees%20Celsius%2C%20a%20threshold%20which%2C%20once%20crossed%2C%20could%20%E2%80%9Cunleash%20far%20more%20severe%20climate%20change%20impacts%2C%20including%20more%20frequent%20and%20severe%20droughts%2C%20heatwaves%2C%20and%20rainfall%E2%80%9D.%20The%20people%20across%20India%E2%80%99s%20rural%20pockets%20have%20a%20bone%20to%20pick%20with%20it%3B%20the%20shifting%20seasons%20have%20heralded%20uncertainty%20into%20their%20lives.%20But%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20paddy%20farmers%20who%20bear%20the%20brunt%20%E2%80%94%20rice%20covers%2069%20percent%20of%20the%20cultivable%20area%3B%20unseasonal%20rains%20incapacitate%20their%20farming%20patterns.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20harvest%20these%20days%20is%20less%20than%20half%20of%20what%20they%20previously%20achieved%2C%E2%80%9D%20Soumya%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20thing%20is%20clear%3A%20despite%20India%E2%80%99s%20hinterland%20experiencing%20some%20semblance%20of%20a%20climate%20crisis%2C%20many%20lack%20the%20vocabulary%20to%20articulate%20it.%20And%20it%20is%20not%20their%20fault%2C%20says%20Jagadish%20Thaker%2C%20a%20senior%20lecturer%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Queensland%2C%20Australia%2C%20and%20principal%20investigator%20of%20a%202023%20survey%20by%20the%20Yale%20Program%20on%20Climate%20Change%20Communication%20(YPCCC)%2C%20which%20indicated%20that%20more%20than%2090%20percent%20of%20Indians%20are%20concerned%20about%20global%20warming.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20opinion%2C%20%E2%80%9Ca%20lack%20of%20awareness%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20mean%20people%20are%20not%20worried%20about%20it%20%5Bclimate%20change%5D.%20It%20means%20that%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20that%20it%20is%20called%20global%20warming%20and%20that%20it%20is%20caused%20by%20human%20activities.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20bridging%20this%20ecological%20literacy%20chasm%20are%20youth%20like%20Soumya%2C%20who%20are%20venturing%20into%20the%20fringes%20of%20Odisha%20armed%20with%20cameras%20and%20ideas.%20Their%20content%20is%20rooted%20in%20native%20script%20to%20help%20India%E2%80%99s%20hinterland%20verbalise%20the%20realities%20unfolding%20in%20the%20fields%20and%20on%20their%20tables.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20creators%20are%20backed%20by%20Momentum%20Shifts%2C%20a%20Bengaluru-based%20initiative%20building%20citizen-facing%20narratives%20for%20system%20changes%2C%20which%20believes%20in%20tailor-made%20content%20and%20humour%20being%20channelled%20into%20tackling%20ecological%20issues.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20portable%20refrigerators%20to%20solar-powered%20homes%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThink%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Etumba%20%3C%2Fem%3Eas%20an%20eco-friendly%20refrigerator%2C%20Soumya%20urges.%20The%20traditional%20vessel%20chiselled%20out%20of%20bottle%20gourd%20%E2%80%94%20not%20the%20usual%20slender%20ones%2C%20but%20imagine%20one%20comparable%20to%20the%20size%20of%20a%20man%E2%80%99s%20head%20%E2%80%94%20is%20popular%20among%20the%20Chuktia%20Bhunjia%20tribe%20in%20the%20Sunabeda%20Wildlife%20Sanctuary%20of%20Nuapada%20district%20in%20Odisha.%20The%20bottle%20gourd%2C%20harvested%20around%2